Later, it became associated with the songs of the North-Eastern regions of Brazil, first of all, with the improvised genre of the song - repente (repente). Researchers identify several main themes:

1.Social, religious or everyday topics (satirical kurdell);
2. Patriarchal structure of society, injustice, periodic droughts in some regions of the North-East; human and social drama (curdelle of the social cycle);
3.Kurdel on political topics, commenting on the actions of the government;
